| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-1142 — Recovery Inhibition (raworld)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 0f97f699-0e53-5f2d-b61e-1ff89bcf2975"
